    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make GCSE Citizenship mandatory in Secondary Schools",
        "additional_details": "Citizenship is already a required subject at KS4, however requiring students to study the GCSE could:\r\n- Make young people even more informed about political affairs\r\n- Increase political participation and voter turnout.\r\n- Aid the awareness of young people and helps them to become more active citizens.\r\n- Reduce the appeal of extremist ideologies and promoting a better understanding of the democratic process.",
        "background": "All Key Stage 4 students should be required to take GCSE Citizenship. ",
